# Frozen test-vector bytes must never be EOL-normalized. Files under
# test-vectors/ are pinned by test-vectors/SHA256SUMS; any autocrlf newline
# conversion would silently corrupt the frozen set. In-repo attributes override
# every contributor's local git config so the published bytes are the bytes
# everyone gets.
test-vectors/** -text
test-vectors/**/*.cose binary
test-vectors/**/*.bin  binary
